Pretend that nothing is wrong
假裝一切順利

1129
01:52:34,710 --> 01:52:36,200
Open your eyes
請睜開眼

1130
01:52:36,410 --> 01:52:38,430
And look for light
尋找光

1131
01:52:40,350 --> 01:52:43,220
What did it leave behind
那一天留下了什麼

1132
01:52:43,430 --> 01:52:46,190
What did it take from us and wash away
從我們這拿走並抹滅的又是什麼

1133
01:52:46,400 --> 01:52:49,840
It may be long
,路會很長

1134
01:52:50,070 --> 01:52:53,730
But with our hearts start a new
但只要我們重心開始

1135
01:52:53,890 --> 01:52:56,360
And keep it up and not give up
堅持不懈，永不言棄

1136
01:52:56,520 --> 01:53:01,650
With our heads held high
並昂首前行

1137
01:53:08,520 --> 01:53:11,950
You have seen hell and made it back again
你見過地獄 又帶到人間

1138
01:53:12,140 --> 01:53:14,470
How to forget 　We can't forget
怎麼忘 我們忘不了

1139
01:53:14,640 --> 01:53:18,760
The lives that were lost along the way
那些沿途迷失的靈魂

1140
01:53:19,840 --> 01:53:23,570
And then you realize that wherever you go
後來你明瞭 無論到哪

1141
01:53:23,770 --> 01:53:24,970
There you are
既來之則安之

1142
01:53:25,170 --> 01:53:27,090
Time won't stop
時間不停

1143
01:53:27,300 --> 01:53:31,100
So we keep moving on
所以我們永不止步

1144
01:53:31,280 --> 01:53:36,930
Yesterday's night turns to light
昨夜化作光

1145
01:53:37,100 --> 01:53:43,340
Tomorrow's night returns to light
明晚歸於光

1146
01:53:45,030 --> 01:53:49,590
Be the light
要成為光

1147
01:54:00,160 --> 01:54:03,660
Some days just pass by and
有些日子過去就過去了

1148
01:54:04,030 --> 01:54:07,790
Some days are unforgettable
但另一些讓人難忘

1149
01:54:08,090 --> 01:54:10,430
We can't choose the reason why
我們無法選擇答案

1150
01:54:10,800 --> 01:54:14,050
But we can choose what to do from the day after.
但可以抉擇明天

1151
01:54:14,810 --> 01:54:18,860
So with that hope, with that determination
所以懷抱這希望 懷抱這決心

1152
01:54:19,140 --> 01:54:23,440
Let's make tomorrow a brighter and better day
讓我們將明天創造得更加光明與美好

